Anonymous;;2011;;PG-13;;Drama,Thriller;;6.9;;Roland Emmerich;;Rhys Ifans,Vanessa Redgrave,David Thewlis,Sebastian Armesto,Rafe Spall,Edward Hogg,Xavier Samuel,Sam Reid,Jamie Campbell Bower,Joely Richardson,Paolo De Vita,Trystan Gravelle,Robert Emms,Tony Way,Julian Bleach,Derek Jacobi,Alex Hassell,James Garnon;;Anonymous is a political thriller which also involves the question of who actually wrote the plays of William Shakespeare. It follows Edward de Vere, 17th Earl of Oxford (Rhys Ifans), and is set against the backdrop of the succession of Queen Elizabeth I (Vanessa Redgrave) and the Essex Rebellion against her.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1521197/